    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it's in absolute pristine condition inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. It runs like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
