      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the premium leather retains its original factory matte texture and 'new car' scent, with absolutely no creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, and a complete binder of service records is included. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels, this car caters to the most discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
